{
  "stem": "13874.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With the help of that ticket, I got a ticket on the Cunard line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most people at the Kitchener Camp had tickets-- open tickets to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[DRINKS] But after the war broke out, the German lines, the French lines, the Italian lines, and all those which normally came from-- stopped in England and went to the United States, wouldn't stop there anymore.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all the tickets-- Cunard that was the only line which recognized its tickets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had some money to come to the States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many people were in camp with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when their quota number came up, they had no money to pay for the passage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure I understand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You said you came on another ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] But they-- yes, but they recognized their own line tickets, the tickets from their own line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you couldn't come on the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't-- The Queen Mary, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Queen Mary is a troop ship now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you came-- you were able to come on another ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I came on another ship on the Cunard line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I landed in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was too numb to think anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a period for me where I was just drifting along.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not enthusiastic about anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just shuffled along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "21 At that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, 22.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My uncle and my brother had come before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were able to get directly out of Germany, get their quota number in October of '39.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a month and a half after the war broke out in Europe, where many people were trapped in the other parts [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were [INAUDIBLE] faster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Holland still was a neutral country.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
